result.title: Invitation to the CodeChef SnackDown 2015 Round 1C (final qualification round) on CodeChef
result.content:
CodeChef invites you to participate in the CodeChef SnackDown Round 1C, which is final qualification round before proceeding to the elimination round.

Time: 7th June 2015 (2130 hrs) to 7th June 2015 (2330 hrs). (Indian Standard Time — +5:30 GMT) — Check out the local time in your City/Time Zone here.

Details: http://www.codechef.com/SNCK2015

Registration: It is a team contest, so you need to register your teams first to take part in the contest. To register your team, login to your CodeChef account and go to: http://snackdown.codechef.com/register. If you don't have a CodeChef account, get one here. Please note that the registrations closes one hour before the contest.

  • Problem Setters : I_lost_my_handle (Praveen Dhinwa)and sentinel45 (Ankit Srivastava)
  • Editorialist: kevinsogo (Kevin Atenzia)
  • Problem Tester: kevinsogo (Kevin Atenzia) and Cherrytree (Sergey Kulik)
  • Contest Admin: I_lost_my_handle (Praveen Dhinwa)
  • Russian Translator : Cherrytree (Sergey Kulik)
  • Mandarin Translator: gediiiiiii (Gedi Zheng)
  • Vietnamese Translator: khanhptnk (Khanh Xuan Nguyen)

It promises to deliver on an interesting set of algorithmic problems with something for all.

Note: Participants who have qualified for elimination round are not allowed to take part in the Round 1C.

Good Luck! Hope to see you participating.
